  "text": "sfc-playground - syntax errors shows _raise stacktrace  instead of parser error message.\n\n### Version\r\n3.1.4\r\n\r\n### Reproduction link\r\n[sfc playground syntax error](https://sfc.vuejs.org/#eyJBcHAudnVlIjoiPHRlbXBsYXRlPlxuICA8aDE+e3sgbXNnIH19PC9oMT5cbjwvdGVtcGxhdGU+XG5cbjxzY3JpcHQgc2V0dXA+XG5jb25zdCBhL2Jcbjwvc2NyaXB0PiAifQ==)\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce\r\nedit a file to have a syntax error.\r\n\r\n### What is expected?\r\nshow actual parse error message.\r\n`\"Unexpected token (5:0)\"`\r\n\r\n### What is actually happening?\r\nshowing internal parser stack trace without error message.\r\n\r\n<img src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/8693091/125176667-4d6f7100-e1a3-11eb-866c-2dadfd207758.png\" width=400 />\r\n\r\nregression\r\n\r\n<!-- generated by vue-issues. DO NOT REMOVE -->",
